In terminal type 

tsc --init 

to create config file for typescript


in tsconfig.json file 

most of the settings were commented out

target   ------ specifies the js code version we get after it has been complied from ts 

under modules  

rootDir   ------ specifies the ts file directory


under emit


outDir  ------ represents the js file directory    mostly we give directory name as dist or distributable folder


removeComments  ---- it removes the comments in the js code which has been added in the ts file. 

noEmitOnError  ----- By default if there is any error in ts file , ts compiler will generate javascript file. by enabling it , it will prevent js file to generate if there is any error in ts file.




